# Api.express.ts #

> [![License][license-src]][license-lnk]
> [![Travis][travis-src]][travis-lnk]
> [![Coveralls][coveralls-src]][coveralls-lnk]
> [![Releases][releases-src]][releases-lnk]
> [![Pull Requests][pullrequest-src]][pullrequest-lnk]
> [![Issues][issues-src]][issues-lnk]

# Setup #

```
npm install -g yarn
yarn install -g ts-node
yarn install -g typescript@2.x.x
yarn install
```

# Usage #

```
yarn run (cmd)
```

* `cmd` is a command from the lists below

```
ts-node run --host=(host) --https=(https) --http=(http)
```

* `host` is the host to bind
* `https` is the https port to bind
* `http` is the http port to bind

# Commands #

| Command           | Description                                                           |                                                |
|-------------------|-----------------------------------------------------------------------|------------------------------------------------|
|                   |                                                                       |                                                |
| `start`           | __alias__ for `serve`                                                 |                                                |
| `serve`           | serve `/src` using ts-node                                            | [http://localhost:3080](http://localhost:3080) |
| `serve:log`       | __alias__ for `serve` with logs                                       |                                                |
| `serve:log:bak`   | __alias__ for `serve` with logs in background                         |                                                |
| `serve:analyze`   | serve `/doc/analyze` using http-server                                | [http://localhost:8080](http://localhost:8080) |
| `serve:coverage`  | serve `/doc/coverage` using http-server                               | [http://localhost:8080](http://localhost:8080) |
| `serve:dist`      | serve `/dist` using http-server                                       | [http://localhost:8080](http://localhost:8080) |
| `serve:doc`       | serve `/doc/typedoc` using http-server                                | [http://localhost:8080](http://localhost:8080) |
|                   |                                                                       |                                                |
| `doc`             | run `documentation generation` to `/doc/typedoc` using typedoc        |                                                |
| `lint`            | run `static analysis` to `/doc/analyze` using tslint                  |                                                |
|                   |                                                                       |                                                |
| `test`            | __alias__ for `test:all`                                              |                                                |
| `test:one (test)` | run one `unit test` using mocha                                       |                                                |
| `test:all`        | run all `unit tests` using mocha                                      |                                                |
|                   |                                                                       |                                                |

